# Changelog

## [2.1.0] - 2026-03-14
- Improved support for multiple devices:
  - Bluethoot
  - I2C
  - BMS
- Scripts:
  - Support startup scripts
  - API for running scripts
- Increased precision of
  - ADC sensors
  - Analog pressure sensor
- Read Open Therm OEM error code.
- Added Wake On LAN sender.
- Support BMS automation on battery level change.
- New MQTT burst rate limit logic.
- SHT20 fixes and improvements.

## [2.0.0] - 2025-12-15
- OTA Updates
- The firmware can be updated over the Internet, using tftp. Support for autoupdates.
- OpenTherm gas consumpton
- New logic for calculating gas consumption of attached OpenTherm device.
- TFTP Client
- Transition from TFTP server to TFTP client.
- New FS copy and move commands
- The copy command supports tftp source or destination file.
- Bug fixes and code cleanups

## [1.0.0] - 2025-11-11
- Initial release

